OL,3,CThames Water fined for 'unjustified'
OL,4,Cdividend payments to shareholders
OL,6,FThames Water has been fined #18.2
OL,7,Fmillion by regulator, Ofwat, over
OL,8,F'unjustified' dividend payments to
OL,9,Fshareholders.
OL,11,FOfwat said the fine was for paying
OL,12,F#158.3 million in dividends to
OL,13,Fshareholders in October 2023 and March
OL,14,F2024, which Ofwat says breached
OL,15,Fcondition P30 of its licence.
OL,17,FThe regulator said it will claw back
OL,18,F#131.3 million of the payments so it
OL,19,Fdoes not come out of customer bills.
