OL,3,CThames Water fined for 'unjustified'
OL,4,Cdividend payments to shareholders
OL,6,FIn documents released by Ofwat, Thames
OL,7,FWater claimed the payments were
OL,8,Fnecessary to ensure it had ongoing
OL,9,Faccess to debt markets.
OL,11,FOfwat disagreed with this assessment,
OL,12,Fsaying the payments resulted in 'the
OL,13,Fextraction of value' from Thames Water.
OL,15,FThames Water also told Ofwat the
OL,16,Fpayments were 'in the best interests
OL,17,Fof its customers and the environment',
OL,18,Fwhich Ofwat said it was 'not convinced
OL,19,Fby'.
