OL,3,CThames Water fined for 'unjustified'
OL,4,Cdividend payments to shareholders
OL,6,FThe regulator also said it considers
OL,7,Fthe contravention of Thames Water's
OL,8,Fobligation to be 'serious' and said
OL,9,Fthe payments were not trivial.
OL,11,FIt is the first time the regulator has
OL,12,Ftaken enforcement action against
OL,13,FThames Water over its dividends
OL,14,Fpayments.
OL,16,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "We
OL,17,Ftake our licence obligations very
OL,18,Fseriously, including those relating to
OL,19,Fthe declaration and payment of
OL,20,Fdividends.
