OL,3,CThames Water fined for 'unjustified'
OL,4,Cdividend payments to shareholders
OL,6,F"The dividends were declared following
OL,7,Fa consideration of the Company's legal
OL,8,Fand regulatory obligations and its
OL,9,Fdividend policy has been updated to
OL,10,Freflect the requirements of Licence
OL,11,FCondition P30.
OL,13,F"Consequently, we disagree with
OL,14,FOfwat's decision and we will be
OL,15,Fproviding a comprehensive response to
OL,16,Ftheir consultation in due course.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
