OL,3,CThames Water fined for 'unjustified'
OL,4,Cdividend payments to shareholders
OL,6,F"No distributions have been made to
OL,7,Fexternal shareholders of the group and
OL,8,Fthey have not taken an external
OL,9,Fdividend since 2017 to prioritise
OL,10,Finvestment in improving service for
OL,11,Fcustomers and to protect the
OL,12,Fenvironment.
OL,14,F"Our plans assume no external
OL,15,Fdividends to shareholders until at
OL,16,Fleast 2030, to support our turnaround."
